The '''Vantom''' is a {{2|Bosses|Boss}} found in the {{2|Overgrowth}}.

== Pattern ==
{{Intents|Vantom|2}}
The Vantom cycles through its four moves in a fixed order, repeating forever:
# {{Int|Vantom|Ink Blot||2}}
# {{Int|Vantom|Inky Lance||2}}
# {{Int|Vantom|Dismember||2}}
# {{Int|Vantom|Prepare||2}}

== Notes ==
* The Vantom begins combat with 9 stacks of {{BD|Slippery||2}}, which causes it to take only 1 HP of damage per hit for the first 9 times it loses HP. Multi-hit attacks are effective at removing {{BD|Slippery||2}} stacks quickly.
* {{Int|Vantom|Prepare||2}} grants 2 {{BD|Strength||2}} each cycle, so the Vantom's damage increases steadily over the fight.
* {{Int|Vantom|Dismember||2}} shuffles 3 {{C|Wound||2}} cards into your discard pile. {{C|Wound||2}} cards are {{KW|Unplayable||2}} and clog your hand.

